=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_Latch_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark clean sound, with fm_or_inharmonic oscillator character around 393 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, and filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 393.1282
  harmonic_decay_rate: -3.2779
  harmonic_regularity: 0.6309
  pitch_clarity: 24.3085
  inharmonicity: 0.4211
  type: fm_or_inharmonic
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -21.2457
  resonance_freq: 710.5957

